Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.34,0:04:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.07,0:04:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}您同意了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.56,0:04:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.41,0:04:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}萬分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.29,0:04:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}等賣出去再謝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.28,0:04:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}每本多少錢 一共幾本？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.36,0:04:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一本200元…印了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.81,0:04:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}200本
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.56,0:04:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.67,0:04:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}搞錯了所以印多了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.89,0:04:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然後…我想盡量賣出去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.60,0:04:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.63,0:04:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}降到150一本 給我二十冊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}跟我們的介紹冊一起賣200
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.55,0:04:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.52,0:05:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你這是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.80,0:05:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}把樣本給我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 是這個意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.99,0:05:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對不起 沒有帶過來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.24,0:05:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}以後記得帶著樣本
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.74,0:05:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}根據你求人的手段 結果會大不相同的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.84,0:05:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}入須學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.12,0:05:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎…怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.29,0:05:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}入須學姐很擅長拜託別人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.87,0:05:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}請您告訴我 該怎麼拜託別人比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:36.71,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.80,0:05:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}聽好了 無論拜託人家什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.29,0:05:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}目的都是促使對方自願去做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.65,0:05:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}促使…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.21,0:06:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為此 就必須給予對方精神上的滿足
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.73,0:06:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然方法有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.40,0:06:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你適用的手段是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.75,0:06:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}期待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.13,0:06:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}期待？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.66,0:06:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對 讓對方認為自己備受期待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.22,0:06:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}讓對方認為…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.55,0:06:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果能做到這點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.04,0:06:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對方就會樂意為你幹活了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.62,0:06:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}幹活…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.46,0:06:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.31,0:06:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是不要把問題弄得太大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.01,0:06:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不要太大…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.76,0:06:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}讓對方覺得那對你來說是件小事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.66,0:06:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}而對他來說倒是有點重要為好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.13,0:06:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還有一點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.69,0:06:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}最好在掩人耳目的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.05,0:06:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}向異性拜託
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.69,0:06:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.64,0:06:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}快點把社刊拿來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.31,0:06:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.90,0:06:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝指教！
