Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.73,0:07:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一包100啊 客官
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.46,0:07:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.12,0:07:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好帥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.42,0:07:51.10,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拿著這個去賣搞不好不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.31,0:07:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那拿2包餅乾來換也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.12,0:07:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}現在買社刊附送這把手槍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.76,0:07:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.31,0:08:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啵！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.48,0:08:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那 給你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.73,0:08:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為表南瓜的感謝之意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.52,0:08:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個也給你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.71,0:08:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}小麥粉？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}Trick or treat！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.47,0:08:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}漫畫研究社引以為傲的行家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.01,0:08:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.58,0:08:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好 完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.96,0:08:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}摩耶…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.66,0:08:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好 要上咯！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.43,0:09:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}摩耶花同學呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.37,0:09:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好像還在忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.33,0:09:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.08,0:09:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}相信她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.64,0:09:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂 福部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是咱這邊的須原 家裡是開料亭的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:16.41,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}註：即日式高級飯店
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.04,0:09:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 那還真是厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.42,0:09:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你就好好加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.30,0:09:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}再見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好好加油呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.22,0:09:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼 下面是這次比賽的入圍者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.67,0:09:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}第一組 好味隊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.52,0:09:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}第二組 海市蜃樓隊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.03,0:09:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}第三組 天文社隊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.52,0:09:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還有 第四組 古籍研究社隊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.15,0:10:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}規則為各隊三人一組
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.80,0:10:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}每個人有20分鐘時間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.11,0:10:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}20分鐘後與下一個人交換
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.40,0:10:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在其中一個人烹飪時
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.93,0:10:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要是和其他人搭話就算犯規
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.82,0:10:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}請務必注意這點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.15,0:10:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}福部同學要做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.00,0:10:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個問題問得好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.56,0:10:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}福部特製海鮮炒飯是也
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.31,0:10:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}話說米飯得要先煮好才行…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.47,0:10:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那福部同學是要做最後的大將咯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.96,0:10:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不…我是最開始的前鋒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.46,0:10:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}反正現在也做不了海鮮炒飯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.58,0:10:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我選哪個都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.46,0:10:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.09,0:10:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}各隊伍每個人做一道菜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.69,0:10:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}食材在中間的籃子裡 先到先得
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.85,0:10:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}萬一沒有材料了 我們也允許在校園範圍內的食材補給
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.54,0:10:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那請擔任前鋒的選手！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.56,0:11:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}On your kitchen！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.72,0:11:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好嘞！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.45,0:11:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那就開始吧！Wild！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.93,0:11:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}Fire！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.72,0:11:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}Fire…
Comment: 0,0:11:27.55,0:11:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.99,0:11:30.00,shisseki,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1249,26)\blur1}秋分\N\N八月中，分者半也，此當九十日之半，故謂之分。
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.79,0:11:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}Wild Fire開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.12,0:11:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}各隊究竟會向我們展現出怎麼樣的料理呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.14,0:11:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真令人期待
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.84,0:11:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}噢 古籍研究社隊將小魚乾的頭和內臟都分別處理乾淨了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.87,0:11:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}料理得多麼細緻啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.29,0:11:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}您覺得如何呢 社長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.98,0:11:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是相當重要的準備工作 副社長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.00,0:11:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海市蜃樓隊準備了蛤蜊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.23,0:12:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要做蘿蔔味增湯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.33,0:12:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 福部同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.02,0:12:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那可不行 蘿蔔還沒削皮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.71,0:12:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}福…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.21,0:12:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不行 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.06,0:12:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}提醒他就犯規了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.74,0:12:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}蘿蔔…皮…皮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.97,0:12:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}福部同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.40,0:12:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 他發現了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.92,0:12:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 要一塊一塊的削皮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.49,0:12:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 糟了 熱水要溢出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.02,0:12:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}古籍研究社隊的菜看起來會花上一段時間啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.02,0:12:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}像是莫比烏斯帶一樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.02,0:12:38.02,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}註：是一種拓撲圖形 只有一個面和一個邊界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.22,0:12:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.96,0:12:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}現在還不知道各隊正在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.80,0:12:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}噢 古籍研究社隊似乎有些躊躇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.33,0:12:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.78,0:12:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是豬肉醬湯！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.58,0:13:01.60,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}噢 好味隊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.74,0:13:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是傳統的肉湯吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.27,0:13:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}照這個速度會趕不上的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.14,0:13:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}各位前鋒的選手 時間差不多要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.41,0:13:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}5 {\alpha&HFF\t(756,756,\alpha&H00)}4 {\alpha&HFF\t(2174,2174,\alpha&H00)}3 {\alpha&HFF\t(2980,2980,\alpha&H00)}2 {\alpha&HFF\t(4200,4200,\alpha&H00)}1
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.50,0:13:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}Change Element！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.46,0:13:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}抱歉 只做了一道菜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.12,0:13:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒問題的 交給我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.68,0:13:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拜託你了 千反田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.47,0:13:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這實在是太厲害了 古籍研究社的中堅選手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.55,0:13:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}削皮技術精妙絕倫！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.97,0:13:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}蘿蔔真正的身姿…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.86,0:13:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}呀 實在太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.78,0:13:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}彷佛被污染的河川也能得以淨化一般的神技
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.70,0:13:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然只是在削皮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.70,0:13:37.38,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}註：日語裡的河川和皮同音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.47,0:13:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好厲害 這就做完一道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.78,0:13:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 結果還是那個千反田啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.73,0:13:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}古籍研究社竟然在搓米！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.49,0:13:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}並且毫不猶豫的把僅限6升的水給倒掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.94,0:13:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為了煮出美味的米飯 而抱以必死的決心了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.33,0:14:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}噢 天文社的中堅選手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.19,0:14:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那是什麼 在做什麼菜啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.52,0:14:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}過激地燃燒啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.51,0:14:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}另一邊 古籍研究社隊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.28,0:14:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是擬製豆腐燒嗎 真是家鄉的味道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.28,0:14:12.60,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}註：即ぎせ焼き 把豆腐和其他食材混合再重新做成豆腐的形狀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.65,0:14:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}Hiromi！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.27,0:14:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}擬製豆腐燒什麼的聽都沒聽過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.72,0:14:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}接下來是海市蜃樓隊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.83,0:14:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}他們的照燒鰤魚已經漸入佳境！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.36,0:14:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}Brilliant！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.47,0:14:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}古籍研究社隊的擬製豆腐燒似乎已經完工了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.92,0:14:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}感覺肚子都餓起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.51,0:14:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這位中堅究竟是何方神聖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.36,0:14:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這可是富農千反田家的千金
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.05,0:14:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}千反田愛瑠是也 給我記好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.30,0:14:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}另一邊 天文社社
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.01,0:14:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還在做他們的前衛料理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.01,0:14:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fs35\pos(723,655)}黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.97,0:14:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}給黑暗吞沒吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.86,0:14:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}古籍研究社隊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}將煮過的馬鈴薯用澱粉勾芡 放進了搗碗裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.52,0:14:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這回打算做薯餅嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.02,0:14:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}手法真嫻熟啊 古籍研究社隊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.15,0:14:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可 似乎有些不妙啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.50,0:14:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不妙 怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.83,0:15:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}古籍研究社隊 提示可是犯規的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.94,0:15:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不行啊 完全沒懂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.66,0:15:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}40分鐘過去了 接下來請換上大將吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}福部同學 怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.68,0:15:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好厲害啊 千反田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.66,0:15:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我都不知道你廚藝這麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.43,0:15:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我很喜歡下廚的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.04,0:15:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 厲害厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.72,0:15:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.55,0:15:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.02,0:15:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊！食材都用光了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.16,0:15:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}摩耶花 抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.72,0:15:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼終於迎來大將決戰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.83,0:16:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}畫好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.74,0:16:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不好意思 麻煩讓一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.98,0:16:20.35,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}噢 好味隊準備用蘋果來做甜點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.95,0:16:23.41,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}慢慢雕出小兔子的形狀了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.12,0:16:27.36,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}古籍研究社的大將還沒現身嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.46,0:16:34.66,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好味隊除了兔子還雕起花來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.54,0:16:38.76,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}將大將還未現身的古籍研究社遠拋在後
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.93,0:16:42.58,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好味隊已經做好了甜點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.47,0:16:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}摩耶花
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.00,0:16:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼！居然有位穿著便服的女生進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.89,0:17:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是古籍研究社隊的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.39,0:17:01.91,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是古籍研究社隊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.40,0:17:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}－摩耶花\N －摩耶花同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.71,0:17:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是古籍研究社 古籍研究社隊的大將終於來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.94,0:17:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼 古籍研究社隊 一波未平一波又起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.56,0:17:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}食材已經所剩無幾了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.61,0:17:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要是什麼都做不出來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.13,0:17:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}大將的分數只能是0分
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.65,0:17:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一路上表現出彩的古籍研究社
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只能到此為止了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.55,0:17:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就這麼點…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.32,0:17:47.22,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}古籍研究社隊 獲得一個小洋蔥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.36,0:17:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.86,0:17:51.88,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可是 這麼個小洋蔥又能做出什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.06,0:17:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}已經沒有主意了嗎 只是呆呆站著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.52,0:17:56.74,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼辦 古籍研究社
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.80,0:17:59.40,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼都不做的話就要失去資格咯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.98,0:18:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.28,0:18:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這些東西能做出什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.49,0:18:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}摩耶花同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.94,0:18:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只有這麼點食材 準備怎麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.01,0:18:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.99,0:18:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你以為是誰的錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.44,0:18:19.46,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}古籍研究社大將 一籌莫展啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.40,0:18:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}做好了 海市蜃樓隊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.56,0:18:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是蛋包飯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.81,0:18:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好好想想 好好想想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.75,0:18:37.92,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}古籍研究社隊 只能到此為止了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.42,0:18:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}應該…應該還有辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.07,0:18:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}古籍研究社隊 無從下手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.83,0:18:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}僅僅剩下10分鐘了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.99,0:18:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只能這樣等到時間結束嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.84,0:18:54.91,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}里志
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.54,0:19:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}剛才是不是有人叫你的名字啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.07,0:19:02.34,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}里志
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.84,0:19:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你聽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.34,0:19:06.31,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}天文社隊 想要用香蕉做湯底嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.07,0:19:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.22,0:19:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.49,0:19:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.11,0:19:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}請安靜一下好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.25,0:19:12.50,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}里志！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.92,0:19:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是折木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.63,0:19:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在那裡 社團活動室
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.73,0:19:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}里志
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.92,0:19:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼 發生啥事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.39,0:19:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}里志 來我這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.72,0:19:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}到我正下方來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.93,0:19:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}給我動作快點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.21,0:19:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}福部同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.31,0:19:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.42,0:19:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.08,0:19:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}接好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.10,0:20:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}接得好！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.02,0:20:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那…這是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.23,0:20:12.66,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}古籍研究社隊的先鋒回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.53,0:20:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}摩耶花
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.66,0:20:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.96,0:20:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}噢 這是要準備逆轉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.02,0:20:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}難道那是小麥粉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.41,0:20:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}規則允許範圍內 沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.50,0:20:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.18,0:20:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還剩7分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.17,0:20:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}WILDFIRE 其他隊伍已經進入尾聲了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.18,0:20:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}古籍研究社終於開始行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.89,0:20:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在這個如此不利的情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.02,0:20:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}到底會讓我們見識到怎樣的戰鬥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.12,0:20:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我很在意= =
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.47,0:20:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}居然拿出了北國紅蝦的頭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.45,0:20:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}她葫蘆裡到底是賣的什麼藥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.98,0:20:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}天婦羅？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.96,0:20:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}原來如此 是天婦羅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.55,0:21:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好 WILDFIRE僅剩5分鐘了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.04,0:21:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我說 料理研究社的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.55,0:21:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你至少也得準備圓勺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.28,0:21:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拿到圓勺的古籍研究社 進入到下一階段
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.73,0:21:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}急起直追啊 古籍研究社
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.95,0:21:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如怒濤般的奮起直追想要反敗為勝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.36,0:21:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}天婦羅蓋飯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.42,0:21:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}能趕得及嗎 古籍研究社隊 還有一分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.02,0:21:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好 已經沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.95,0:21:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}撈起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.81,0:21:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}盛放在碗裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.54,0:22:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}3 2 1
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.81,0:22:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}時間到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.30,0:22:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}YES
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.82,0:22:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.95,0:22:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}摩耶花同學
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.13,0:22:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.98,0:22:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.12,0:22:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.38,0:23:00.22,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼 發表結果
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.30,0:23:02.95,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}獲得優勝的隊伍是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.84,0:23:06.71,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}隊伍 古籍研究社
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.63,0:23:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好累
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.58,0:23:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}炸得不夠久
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.12,0:23:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}既沒有時間又別無選擇 這已經很棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.37,0:23:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}都怪他們沒有準備圓勺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.18,0:23:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要是有圓勺的話就更完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.22,0:23:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}他們去拿那個都花了一分鐘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.26,0:23:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也太傻了 要是沒有圓勺就用別的代替嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.66,0:23:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的是萬分抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.62,0:23:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我們應該是確認過的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.58,0:23:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}都怪我們沒有最後再確認一次
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.66,0:23:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一開始我們也覺得很怪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.06,0:23:43.65,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我先離開下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.77,0:23:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我們也該確認下的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.29,0:23:45.99,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}過去了就過去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.17,0:23:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.57,0:23:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼？
